.TH banner "" "" Command
.PC "Print large letters"
\fBbanner\fR [ \fIargument ... \fR]
.PP
.HS
Print each \fIargument\fR as one line of large-text output.
If no arguments, print each line from stdin as a line of large output.
.HE
.B banner
prints large (seven-character by five-character)
letters on the standard output.
Each
.I argument
produces one large text output line.
If there is no
.IR argument ,
each line from the standard input produces one line of large-text output.
.SH "See Also"
.Xr commands, commands
.Xr libmisc, libmisc
.Xr lpr, lpr
.Xr pr pr
